# Historical Strategy Tester

A Python tool for testing trading strategies on historical market data. Designed for speed, flexibility, and strategy refinement.

## Features
- Load historical data from CSV or API
- Apply custom trading strategies
- Simulate trade entries/exits
- Calculate win rate, profit factor, and other key metrics
- Visualize trades on charts (matplotlib)

## Requirements
- Python 3.8+
- pandas
- matplotlib
- numpy

## Setup
```bash
git clone https://github.com/pocketoptionguru/historical-strategy-tester.git
cd historical-strategy-tester
pip install -r requirements.txt
